    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/5a71b2fb94aa7602a17df1335393907f.poster.avif?t=1770488222\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/5a71b2fb94aa7602a17df1335393907f.webm?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/5a71b2fb94aa7602a17df1335393907f.mp4?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >看着你的火车从一个小小的火车头成长为一台清屏机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/2189f43e1795154ab91ca7730cf38c09.poster.avif?t=1770488222\" width=640 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/2189f43e1795154ab91ca7730cf38c09.webm?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/2189f43e1795154ab91ca7730cf38c09.mp4?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁新的车厢并发现能够改变游戏规则的协同效应。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/8f9ac9951aca131da2b33ac017922ab1.poster.avif?t=1770488222\" width=640 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/8f9ac9951aca131da2b33ac017922ab1.webm?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/8f9ac9951aca131da2b33ac017922ab1.mp4?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过庞大的升级树来实现自己的目标。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/1649eda1167f66411cba5b50387a816c.poster.avif?t=1770488222\" width=640 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/1649eda1167f66411cba5b50387a816c.webm?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208560/extras/1649eda1167f66411cba5b50387a816c.mp4?t=1770488222\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
